{"tid":229437,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人經歷過精神崩潰","createTime":"2017-05-04T15:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T15:11:32.000Z","uid":55296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f142fafc92614a948ed2383a224e27d284d66808","tid":229437,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:04:41.000Z","msg":"兩年前開始有胃病 發病時會胃脹 作嘔<br />\n慢慢唔想出街食飯 搭車會驚病發<br />\n見客嗰時尤其要忍好驚嘔出嚟<br />\n<br />\n今日為左下午見客避免胃脹無點食過嘢<br />\n結果放左工都好胃痛<br />\n突然間積積埋埋嘅焦慮爆發晒出嚟<br />\n唔知做咩不停喊 個精神好亂 仲難受過個胃<br />\n或者係個胃影響精神 精神影響胃啦<br />\n<br />\n你地點紓緩精神上嘅爆發<br />\n好似一直以嚟嘅焦慮去晒極點咁 唔識處理<br />\n開始明白有情緒病嘅人點解會自殘、情緒不穩定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9b4ad624262380727baa5068f8684ccfa62e50","tid":229437,"uid":74015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}